Package: Geopopr
Title: Population geography spatial analysis and visualization 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Gustavo", "Givisiez", , "gh_naves@id.uff.br", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package providing tools for spatial analysis and visualization in population geography, including density calculations, demographic indicators, and map projections. Designed for geographers and demographers working with spatial population data.
